snippet.title: Bonesaw - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1586860?utm_source=youtube_launchtrailer

The official release of Bonesaw will be available on March 5th!

Gamble your fingers against the devil and his bloodthirsty saw in this turn-based strategy game. Outsmart your opponent with special abilities, or test your luck as you defy the odds to escape eternal damnation!
